{
  "stem": "12904.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then I wanted to come back to the Midwest because my mother was not well and I felt I wanted to be back in the area at least.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't particularly want to come to St.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Louis, but I applied to Elgin State Hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I did like psychiatric occupational therapy better than the physical part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And took the job as chief occupational therapist at Elgin State Hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I stayed there for five years, and then, when I was married, moved to Chicago and then to Gary, Indiana.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Lived in Gary, that's where my godson was born.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I took-- well, I worked for five years-- I had sort of established myself-- I thought five years was long enough, at that time, to be in a job.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Later on I realized I-- I had a vested interest in retirement, but at that time I didn't think about that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so I moved, then, to Gary, Indiana and lived there for a couple of years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then we lived in Chicago where I was married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I drove every day from Chicago to Gary to my job, which was-- then heading a-- a clinic actually, for preschool handicapped children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And since I had had training in early childhood education, I thought I would do that, combine my knowledge in child psychology and so on, and direct that clinic.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Which was a good experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was in Gary, but it was a long drive from Chicago to Gary, but my husband was working in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was not well, already, at the time, and had a heart condition of which he then died.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
